        href=&quot;./../../soa.rup_soma/workproducts/soa_svce_model_svce_spec_37E89A91.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;{20F06B5E-95D5-422C-AB68-7C213D28533A}&quot;>Artifact: Service Specification&lt;/a>, whether candidate or exposed,&#xD;
        may be traced to these business goals using mechanisms defined by the requirements tool.&#xD;
